# Connecting nodes with relations
<https://example.com/HubNode> noria:connectedTo <https://example.com/HubSwitch> .
<https://example.com/HubSwitch> noria:linksTo <https://example.com/connection1> .

<https://example.com/Resource1> noria:connectedTo <https://example.com/Firewall1> .
<https://example.com/Firewall1> noria:linksTo <https://example.com/connection2> .

<https://example.com/RouterA> noria:connectedTo <https://example.com/LoadBalancer1> .
<https://example.com/LoadBalancer1> noria:linksTo <https://example.com/connection4> .

<https://example.com/Multiplexer1> noria:connectedTo <https://example.com/SuperSwitch> .
<https://example.com/SuperSwitch> noria:linksTo <https://example.com/connection5> .

<https://example.com/HubNode> noria:connectedTo <https://example.com/HighDegreeNode> .
<https://example.com/HighDegreeNode> noria:linksTo <https://example.com/connection3> .

<https://example.com/HighDegreeNode> noria:connectedTo <https://example.com/CentralNode> .
<https://example.com/CentralNode> noria:linksTo <https://example.com/connection6> .

# End of graph

